Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.tree

Class AbstractTree<E>

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.tree.AbstractTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements stored in the tree
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tree<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractBinaryTree
public abstract class AbstractTree<E> extends Object implements Tree<E>
A skeletal implementation of the Tree abstract data type. This class provides implementation for common methods that can be implemented the same no matter what specific type of concrete data structure is used to implement the tree abstract data type.
Author:
Dr. King, Jeremiah Knizley
